snippet.title: ACE COMBAT 7: SKIES UNKNOWN - Multiplayer Trailer | PS4, PSVR, X1, PC
snippet.description:
Watch your six when ACE COMBAT 7: SKIES UNKNOWN releases Jan. 18th on PS4 & Xbox One and Feb. 1st on PC: http://bandainam.co/AceCombat7 #AceCombat7 #BandaiNamco #VideoGames

The skies of Strangereal may contain the unknown but you're definitely not by yourself out there! Take on other ace pilots in the free for all Battle Royal mode or join a squad in Team Deathmatch.
